relatedNodes.source: This web page is for demonstration purposes, to show common accessibility errors.
A trip to Mars starts in your imagination. Are you bold enough, brave enough, crazy enough? We are. You belong on Mars with crazies like us. Most of us don't bite. Much.
Step out of your comfort zone, and into a rocket with enough fuel to blast a Manhattan-sized crater if it explodes. But it won't. Probably.
If you're serious about traveling to Mars - really serious - then prepare your last will and testament, and book a trip!
Expect violent turbulence, bone-crushing g-forces, muscle atrophy, and certain death (hey, everyone's death is certain at some point, right?).
Book select MarStar Crater tickets and enjoy 10% off the Crater Adventures Pass. Safety not guaranteed. Book your MarStar Crater Package today to save!
